00:09:13.150 --> 00:09:16.010
We wanted to leverage
our existing structure

00:09:16.010 --> 00:09:19.360
but be a little more deliberate,
so we could take advantages

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:22.640
of the opportunities that
we had and connecting

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:25.680
the structure and
more logical ways.

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:27.880
So again, the reason why
I'm underscoring this point

00:09:27.880 --> 00:09:31.880
is that many of you
may have a product,

00:09:31.880 --> 00:09:34.020
you may have a general
structure, an architecture

00:09:34.020 --> 00:09:36.340
that you feel pretty happy with.

00:09:36.340 --> 00:09:39.180
And you like us, we
didn't feel like we

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:41.200
needed to reinvent the
wheel on everything.

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:43.459
We wanted to be very tactical.

