For instance, one of the
structural opportunities

00:09:45.500 --> 00:09:47.862
we wanted to look at
was our card system.

00:09:47.862 --> 00:09:49.570
If you're familiar
with the Play product,

00:09:49.570 --> 00:09:52.100
we obviously
leverage like Google

00:09:52.100 --> 00:09:55.140
does the card metaphor
to represent content.

00:09:55.140 --> 00:09:59.350
5 So the material framework
was giving us an opportunity

00:09:59.350 --> 00:10:02.740
to do really great things
like the dynamic shadowing,

00:10:02.740 --> 00:10:06.290
and the transformation
from scene to scene.

00:10:06.290 --> 00:10:08.280
And so we really
wanted to use this

00:10:08.280 --> 00:10:10.880
as an example of one
structural component

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.240
that we saw as a very
opportunistic way

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:16.550
