structure in isolation.

00:10:25.190 --> 00:10:29.070
We try to avoid the waterfall
process where you identify

00:10:29.070 --> 00:10:30.820
things, it goes
to visual design,

00:10:30.820 --> 00:10:33.360
then to interaction
design, maybe motion,

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:37.250
