in the hands of engineers.

00:10:37.250 --> 00:10:41.210
But the point is we want to
advocate a parallel process

00:10:41.210 --> 00:10:44.930
where this is obviously
dependent on the size

00:10:44.930 --> 00:10:46.570
of your team.

00:10:46.570 --> 00:10:48.770
But we wanted to
advocate a process where

00:10:48.770 --> 00:10:51.230
